{"tid":1352393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇辦法屌醒藍絲，唔好再講乜野有事唔好搵警察呢的on9野","createTime":"2019-07-22T18:48:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T20:07:52.000Z","uid":270533,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0f7587fa491d3cc737d54eb007750857773c2261","tid":1352393,"uid":270533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:48:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SW7sMG4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSW7sMG4.jpg&h=ad6c3f97&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就好似陳欣健呢的on9佬。其實好L多人已經答L過哂，仲要講。好L煩! 有冇辦法將類似回應炸爆藍絲網?<br />\n例如: 警察係出左糧要服務市民架，唔係義工呀！佢做錯野，比市民鬧，有乜出奇?鬧下就唔可以叫佢地做呀？咁你屋企個印傭做錯野，比你鬧完，可唔可以話:Sir/Mum 你咁憎我，有事唔好叫我做。得唔得呀?<br />\n短的嘅: 你班差人，之前又屌的醫護人員左你地，又話要徹警崗，你地受左傷(比人咬手指)唔好去政府醫院呀，笨!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c15ae236e85cb131e24ad1a36cb448070772307","tid":1352393,"uid":270533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:48:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"597d221a06a767e904da52debd8ecc15ed86973c","tid":1352393,"uid":144849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:48:34.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"6c12307563ac25247026f27d24ac0059b61bd148","tid":1352393,"uid":270533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:48:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf990f1d38a2a1b0179df407577d429d267ceb90","tid":1352393,"uid":270533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:48:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75a2382b99ee87b4c39c10b15a40fbf093d5ac34","tid":1352393,"uid":52023,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:5